{
  "stem": "22869.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were a couple of guys who divulged to the world on what's going on in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the pressure on the Germans got bigger and bigger.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I don't remember exactly the time, but it was about towards fall, or maybe October or so in 1944, that they did away with the crematorium.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There were no more mass killings, no more gassing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They stopped that because the Germans felt a little pressure, and they were like losing the wars on all the corners, too.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So they were like scared of us, so that stopped.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And there were no newcomers at this point, either, so the food in camp was scarce.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I became, again, somebody, because now everybody wanted the food that I used to go every day to get.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And so we lived there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I mean, we had the normal life as far as we were not undernourished.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We were not overnourished.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We had our ration of bread that they gave us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Nobody poured it out in the mud like in the early times, like the Russians did.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So like I said, it was enough to sustain yourself.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And nobody in this camp-- not the boys and not the girls-- had-- had a problem as far as sustaining themselves as far as eating.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "There's a-- there's another little incident I'd like to mention before I get to the end of this segment.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "There was a girl in this camp who apparently had a-- secretly an affair with an SS guy.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I can-- I'm not going to mention names, but it-- it was divulged in Israel in all the newspapers, you know, when it came out later.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--I have a-- a wish.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he was in charge of that whole camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
